<doc id="251382" wikidata="Q7911554" url="?curid=251382" title="Valhall">
<text>Valhall is an anglicized form of Old Norse &quot;Valhǫll&quot;, an afterlife &quot;hall of the slain&quot; in Norse mythology, which is more commonly anglicized as &quot;Valhalla&quot;. Otherwise, Valhall may refer to:

*Valhall (band), a Norwegian band
*Valhall oil field, a Norwegian oil field

==See also==
*Valhalla
*Walhalla (disambiguation)</text><links>
